      REPLACE NUD_LUNGHE WITH (M.MAG_QTAML - MAG_GMLIMP)
      REPLACE NUD_QTAMQ  WITH (M.MAG_QTAMQ - MAG_QTAIMP)
      REPLACE NUD_QTAKG  WITH (M.MAG_QTAKG - MAG_GKGIMP)
   ELSE
      REPLACE NUD_LUNGHE WITH V_LENSCA
